               <p>Riches Reed. I am a <rs id="t17721021-59-viclabel285" type="occupation">labourer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17721021-59-victim546 t17721021-59-viclabel285"></join>, and am employed to keep order in <placeName id="t17721021-59-crimeloc286">St. Paul's church</placeName>
