                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17721021-59-off283 t17721021-59-crimeloc286"></join>; the prisoner came into the church as soon as the door was open, and sat upon the bench; I laid my hat down in a nitch there; I took notice the prisoner drew near to where my hat was; I communicated my suspicion to one of the porters; at length I found the prisoner going off with my hat; I followed him; and took my hat from him as he was going to the West door.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I did not intend to steal it; I thought it had been left there by somebody or other who had been sitting there; I took it up meaning to find out the owner. I am a <rs id="t17721021-59-deflabel287" type="occupation">soldier</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17721021-59-defend544 t17721021-59-deflabel287"></join>.</p>
